{05} — FAQ

Got Questions?

Got Questions?

01/

What services do I offer in branding and design?

I specialize in creating impactful logos, brand identities, visual style guides, business cards, letterheads, packaging, and branded merchandise. I also develop consistent brand strategies to enhance clients' presence across various platforms.

02/

Can you refresh or update my existing branding?

Absolutely! I can refine and modernize your existing branding while maintaining its core identity to ensure relevance and consistency across all platforms.

03/

What technologies do you use for web development?

I use modern web technologies such as HTML, CSS, JavaScript, WebGL, and frameworks like React and GSAP for animations and interactions.

04/

How do I handle revisions and feedback?

Revisions and feedback are a crucial part of the process. I typically offer unlimited revisions refine the design based on your input. I ensure clear communication throughout, so your vision is brought to life effectively.

05/

How can we start working together?

You can reach out to discuss your project, and I'll provide a proposal as per to your requirement outlining the process, timeline, and cost. Let's create something amazing!
